# ============================================================
# M5 OUTPUTS
# ============================================================
# Do NOT ignore models/ outputs here.
# M5 outputs are now organized by purpose:
#
# models/reports/      -> report/reviewer summaries
# models/m6_handoff/   -> files for M6 A/B testing
# models/diagnostics/  -> audit/debug outputs
# models/artifacts/    -> M5 model artifacts
#
# If the team later decides not to push customer-level or binary files,
# add explicit ignore rules for models/m6_handoff/ and models/artifacts/.